NUMBER 201
NAME City Gate
MONSTER_GROUP 1
*DESCRIPTION_START
This massive gateway, corroded by salty blasts from the Eastern Waste and coated with a skin of ice, guards the entrance to the city of Fayd. Iron walls extend each way to secure the inhabitants from the barbarism that lies outside. West through the bazaar, a wide street plunges into the city's heart. Commotion, excitement, and the smells of city life reach out to you as people of every race go about their business.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 8 1567
OUTDOOR_OTHER
FIXED_LIGHT
EXIT W 202
EXIT ABOVE 2152
ITEM 0 68 ADJ1=178 ADJ2=169 VAL2=501 UNLOCKED OPEN
IFENTRY
  IFVAR INTNUM6 = 0
    NEWITEM -1 255 ADJ1=181 ADJ2=40
    NEWITEM -1 253 ADJ1=87 ADJ2=40
    NEWITEM -1 217 ADJ1=298 ADJ2=180
    GMMSG Honk! %N is a newbie.
    ECHO PLAYER [Type HELP to access the help system. Type ASSIST to request a gamemaster as soon as one is available. Type ADVICE for hints on getting started.]
    PLREVENT 1
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER You have been given tunic, breeches and boots. Please WEAR them immediately. (WEAR TUNIC, WEAR BREECHES, WEAR TUNIC)
    PLREVENT 1
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER You have also been given a roleplaying OBJECT, which allows you to do enhanced roleplaying actions. TAP the OBJECT to see the rules. Make sure you practice in private.
    EQUAL INTNUM6 2
  	PLREVENT 4
		CONTPLREVENT
		ECHO PLAYER A little voice inside your head says, "Keep going west, young one, keep going west."
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFENTRY
  IFVAR INTNUM6 = 2
    GMMSG Honk! %N is a newbie.
    ECHO PLAYER [Type HELP to access the help system. Type ASSIST to request a gamemaster as soon as one is available. Type ADVICE for hints on getting started.]
		PLREVENT 4
		CONTPLREVENT
		ECHO PLAYER A little voice inside your head says, "Keep going west, young one, keep going west."
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFENTRY -1
  IFVAR INTNUM6 = 1
    EQUAL INTNUM6 3
  ENDIF
ENDIF
